---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Motel Acquisition Audit & Due Diligence | Motel Coach">
  <!-- 1. Risk-Shield Hero -->
  <section class="bg-[#F9F9F8] border-b border-stone-200 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight text-balance">
          The Most Expensive Mistake in Motel Buying is the One You Don&apos;t See.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
          Professional operational due diligence for independent motel acquisitions. We find the hidden leaks in P&amp;Ls, staff structures, and OTA setups before you sign.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
          Whether you are buying your first motel or adding to an existing portfolio, our audit gives you a practitioner-led view of the asset&apos;s true operational health before you commit capital.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm space-y-4">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
            Confidence Metrics
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-stone-700">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between">
              <span class="text-stone-500">Properties audited</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">100+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between">
              <span class="text-stone-500">Regional &amp; metro coverage</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Specialists</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. What We Uncover Grid -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight text-balance mb-10">
        What We Uncover in a Motel Acquisition Audit
      </h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-[#F9F9F8] border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              01
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              Revenue Integrity
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
            Validating the real occupancy versus reported figures, checking rate integrity, and stress-testing RevPAR assumptions against market reality.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#F9F9F8] border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              02
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              Operational Leakage
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
            Identifying wasted spend in staffing, laundry, and utilities, and mapping where daily practices are quietly eroding margin.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#F9F9F8] border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              03
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              Digital Health
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
            Auditing Google Business Profile, website conversion, and OTA commission structures so you understand how the property really attracts and converts demand.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#F9F9F8] border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              04
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400">
              Physical Liability
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
            Highlighting maintenance debt, safety and WHS issues, and capital items that will require near-term investment after settlement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Institutional Inquiry Form -->
  <section class="bg-[#F9F9F8] py-24 border-y border-stone-200">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-2 text-balance">
          Request a Motel Acquisition Audit
        </h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Provide a few details below and we&apos;ll schedule a confidential, practitioner-led review of your target property before you finalise your contract.
        </p>
        <form class="space-y-5" action="/contact" method="get">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1" for="fullName">
                Full Name
              </label>
              <input
                id="fullName"
                name="name"
                type="text"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm text-stone-900 placeholder-stone-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#4A554E] focus:border-transparent"
                placeholder="Your name"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1" for="email">
                Email
              </label>
              <input
                id="email"
                name="email"
                type="email"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm text-stone-900 placeholder-stone-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#4A554E] focus:border-transparent"
                placeholder="you@example.com"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1" for="phone">
                Phone
              </label>
              <input
                id="phone"
                name="phone"
                type="tel"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm text-stone-900 placeholder-stone-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#4A554E] focus:border-transparent"
                placeholder="+61..."
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1" for="settlement">
                Expected Settlement Date
              </label>
              <input
                id="settlement"
                name="settlementDate"
                type="date"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm text-stone-900 placeholder-stone-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#4A554E] focus:border-transparent"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1" for="motelName">
              Motel Name / Location (Optional)
            </label>
            <input
              id="motelName"
              name="motel"
              type="text"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm text-stone-900 placeholder-stone-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#4A554E] focus:border-transparent"
              placeholder="e.g. 40-room coastal motel in NSW"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1" for="concern">
              What is your biggest concern regarding this property?
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="concern"
              name="concern"
              rows="4"
              class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-stone-200 bg-white text-sm text-stone-900 placeholder-stone-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#4A554E] focus:border-transparent"
              placeholder="Tell us what you&apos;re worried about: revenue, staff, systems, maintenance, or something else."
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 bg-[#4A554E] text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-[#3d4640] transition-colors shadow-sm"
          >
            Request Confidential Audit Consultation
          </button>

          <p class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-stone-400">
            <span class="inline-flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-stone-300 text-[9px]">🔒</span>
            <span>All inquiries are handled with 100% practitioner–client confidentiality.</span>
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Benjamin Douglas Bio Snippet -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 border-t border-stone-200 pt-10">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-3">
            Why Benjamin Douglas?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-900 tracking-tight text-balance">
            Practitioner-led due diligence for serious motel buyers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-3 text-sm text-stone-500 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Benjamin Douglas is the Lead Practitioner at Motel Coach and author of <em>The Essential Guide to Motel Management</em>. His background spans operational and commercial leadership across independent motel and hotel groups.
          </p>
          <p>
            He has overseen operations across <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">16+ motels</span>, 10 restaurants, and more than 200 staff, giving him a granular view of where motels leak profit and where they can scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            This audit service is grounded in that experience. It is not a checkbox corporate report — it is a precise, practitioner-led review of the asset you are about to acquire.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

